{
  "number": 83,
  "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
  "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "Woe to those that deal in fraud,-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Those who, when they have to receive by measure from men, exact full measure,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "But when they have to give by measure or weight to men, give less than due.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Do they not think that they will be called to account?-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "On a Mighty Day,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "A Day when (all) mankind will stand before the Lord of the Worlds?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Nay! Surely the record of the wicked is (preserved) in Sijjin.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "And what will explain to thee what Sijjin is?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "(There is) a Register (fully) inscribed.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to those that deny-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Those that deny the Day of Judgment.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "And none can deny it but the Transgressor beyond bounds the Sinner!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "When Our Signs are rehearsed to him, he says, \"Tales of the ancients!\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "By no means! but on their hearts is the stain of the (ill) which they do!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Verily, from (the Light of) their Lord, that Day, will they be veiled.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Further, they will enter the Fire of Hell.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Further, it will be said to them: \"This is the (reality) which ye rejected as false!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Nay, verily the record of the Righteous is (preserved) in 'Illiyin.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "And what will explain to thee what 'Illiyun is?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "(There is) a Register (fully) inscribed,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "To which bear witness those Nearest (to Allah).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Truly the Righteous will be in Bliss:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "On Thrones (of Dignity) will they command a sight (of all things):",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Thou wilt recognise in their faces the beaming brightness of Bliss.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "Their thirst will be slaked with Pure Wine sealed:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "The seal thereof will be Musk: And for this let those aspire, who have aspirations:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "With it will be (given) a mixture of Tasnim:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "A spring, from (the waters) whereof drink those Nearest to Allah.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "Those in sin used to laugh at those who believed,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And whenever they passed by them, used to wink at each other (in mockery);",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And when they returned to their own people, they would return jesting;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And whenever they saw them, they would say, \"Behold! These are the people truly astray!\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "But they had not been sent as keepers over them!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "But on this Day the Believers will laugh at the Unbelievers:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "On Thrones (of Dignity) they will command (a sight) (of all things).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "Will not the Unbelievers have been paid back for what they did?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}